# Component organization for pages

- Keep `src/components/ui/` for reusable primitives only (`Button`, `Card`, variants, utilities).
- Keep `src/components/shared/` for cross-page sections (for example `Nav`).
- For each route, group page-specific sections under a page folder:
  - `src/components/home/`
  - `src/components/about/`
  - future routes should follow the same pattern (for example `src/components/services/`).
- Inside each page folder, organize by section intent, not by date or author (for example `hero`, `story`, `services`, `showcase`, `cta`).
- When adding a new page section, place it in the matching page/section folder and import from `src/pages/<route>.astro`.
- Avoid dumping new page sections at `src/components/` root unless they are truly shared across multiple pages.
